OL,7,FThe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,8,FOmbudsman says the Department for Work
OL,9,Fand Pensions (DWP) failed to
OL,10,Fadequately communicate changes to
OL,11,Fwomen's state pension age, and that
OL,12,Fthose affected are owed compensation.
OL,14,FThe ombudsman has asked Parliament to
OL,15,Fintervene and "act swiftly" to make
OL,16,Fsure a compensation scheme is
OL,17,Festablished.
