OL,7,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,8,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,9,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,10,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,12,FThe age rise came into effect in 2010,
OL,13,Fbut many women weren't informed about
OL,14,Fthe changes until as little as 12
OL,15,Fmonths before they came into force.
OL,17,FWaspi campaigners had called for
OL,18,Fcompensation of #10,000 for all 3.8
OL,19,Fmillion women, but the report
OL,20,Frecommends between #1,000 and #2,950.
