OL,7,FChair of the Waspi group Angela Madden
OL,8,Ftold ITV News: "I only got two year's
OL,9,Fnotice of the state pension age
OL,10,Fchange, and I had already given up a
OL,11,Ffull-time job at that time to spend
OL,12,Ftime with my then ailing mother,
OL,13,Fthere's no way you can undo that
OL,14,Fdecision".
OL,16,FMs Madden said the amount of
OL,17,Fcompensation recommended by the
OL,18,Fombudsman wasn't enough, because many
OL,19,Fwomen experienced "actual financial
OL,20,Flosses".
