OL,7,FTo date, the DWP has not acknowledged
OL,8,Fits failings, nor put things right for
OL,9,Fthose affected, the report said.
OL,11,FThe report found the DWP's handling of
OL,12,Fthe pension age changes meant some
OL,13,Fwomen lost opportunities to make
OL,14,Finformed decisions about their
OL,15,Ffinances.
OL,17,FIt diminished their sense of personal
OL,18,Fautonomy and financial control, the
OL,19,Fombudsman said.
