OL,7,FPHSO chief executive Rebecca
OL,8,FHilsenrath said: "The UK's national
OL,9,Fombudsman has made a finding of
OL,10,Ffailings by DWP in this case, and has
OL,11,Fruled that the women affected are owed
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,F"DWP has clearly indicated that it
OL,15,Fwill refuse to comply. This is
OL,16,Funacceptable. The department must do
OL,17,Fthe right thing and it must be held to
OL,18,Faccount for failure to do so.
