OL,7,F"Complainants should not have to wait
OL,8,Fand see whether DWP will take action
OL,9,Fto rectify its failings.
OL,11,F"Given the significant concerns we
OL,12,Fhave that it will fail to act on our
OL,13,Ffindings, and given the need to make
OL,14,Fthings right for the affected women as
OL,15,Fsoon as possible, we have proactively
OL,16,Fasked Parliament to intervene and hold
OL,17,Fthe department to account.
