OL,7,FSpeaking before the report's release,
OL,8,FHealth Minister Andrea Leadsom said:
OL,9,F"I've had a number of constituents of
OL,10,Fmy own who've talked to me about this
OL,11,Fover the years, and I do completely
OL,12,Funderstand the issue".
OL,14,FLabour's Shadow Work and Pensions
OL,15,FMinister Alison McGovern said: "When
OL,16,Fyou're planning for your retirement
OL,17,Ffuture, you need to understand what
OL,18,Fyou state pension entitlement is going
OL,19,Fto be, and if there are changes the
OL,20,Fgovernment has a responsibility to
OL,21,Fdeal with properly".
